<p>Hello, I am David Zhang (<a href="/resume/" target="_blank">resume</a>), a.k.a crisp or crispgm on the internet.
I am a software engineer of fullstack web development.
I make web products, and contribute to <a href="/project.html">open source community</a>.
I write <a href="/blog.html">blog posts</a> here, and post photos on <a href="https://instagram.com/crispgm" target="_blank">Instagram</a>.</p>

<p>I greatly appreciate minimalism and simplicity. I enjoy photography, reading, coffee, foosball, and Japanese idol groups.</p>

